    "description": "Blockworks is a creative VR block-building sandbox game. Follow instructions or express your creativity and build anything you can imagine with hundreds of blocks and materials. Decorate your room environment. Share your creations on steam workshop.<br><br><strong>Instructions</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/e6fb5273cefa047358df7b3057d7c62c.poster.avif?t=1715870970\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/e6fb5273cefa047358df7b3057d7c62c.webm?t=1715870970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/e6fb5273cefa047358df7b3057d7c62c.mp4?t=1715870970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Follow step by step instructions and build from a selection of built-in or user created sets.<br><br><strong>Sandbox Mode</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/33bd5638dac37852985d511816211b4b.poster.avif?t=1715870970\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/33bd5638dac37852985d511816211b4b.webm?t=1715870970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/33bd5638dac37852985d511816211b4b.mp4?t=1715870970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>All blocks and all materials are at your disposal. You can save your block creations in the library or share them on the game workshop.<br><br><strong>Endless Mode</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/b7c35f44646fa531e3ddb2bbd21e9202.poster.avif?t=1715870970\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/b7c35f44646fa531e3ddb2bbd21e9202.webm?t=1715870970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/b7c35f44646fa531e3ddb2bbd21e9202.mp4?t=1715870970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>No longer limited by table size, you have an infinite area to build on. Place the blocks on the studs on the ground.<br><br><strong>Decorations</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/6bde939ca1ac6e6b88e1f806132395da.poster.avif?t=1715870970\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/6bde939ca1ac6e6b88e1f806132395da.webm?t=1715870970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825970/extras/6bde939ca1ac6e6b88e1f806132395da.mp4?t=1715870970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Decorate your room with your creations<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>- 300+ of different blocks<br>- 50+ materials<br>- 4 game modes<br>- 1000+ of community builds<br><br>Join our official Discord for more fun outside the game!",
